item.title: Confessions from the Trade: Balancing Short Sessions and Unforeseen Consequences
item.description: I know many girls charge more for short session than longer ones, for instance, $200 for 30 minutes and $300 for an hour, but I didn’t, because, to be honest, a 15 minutes session is just as good as a 60 minutes booking. Come, cum and go in 15 minutes feels like I’m doing CrossFit or HIIT yet it can feed me 5 times of banana blossom and 10 times of chatime so how can I not like it.
